92
00:08:47,770 --> 00:08:49,330
Kenapa?

93
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:53,890
Kurasa dia mengharap sesuatu yang baru dariku.

94
00:08:53,890 --> 00:08:55,780
Dia ingin kami berubah.

95
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:58,770
